<paragraph id="8BF236CBC50BFFECFF5CFEAE780FFE90" blockId="14.[151,1134,322,757]" box="[151,546,322,348]" pageId="14" pageNumber="23">
<heading id="D0BA81A7C50BFFECFF5CFEAE780FFE90" box="[151,546,322,348]" fontSize="11" level="2" pageId="14" pageNumber="23" reason="2">
<taxonomicName id="4C4D4D48C50BFFECFF5CFEAE780FFE90" authority="(Hubner, 1813)" baseAuthorityName="Hubner" baseAuthorityYear="1813" box="[151,546,322,348]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Xestia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="stigmatica">
<emphasis id="B939EAD9C50BFFECFF5CFEAE780FFE90" bold="true" box="[151,546,322,348]" pageId="14" pageNumber="23">
<emphasis id="B939EAD9C50BFFECFF5CFEAE7B48FE90" bold="true" box="[151,357,322,348]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="23">Xestia stigmatica</emphasis>
(Hübner, 1813)
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BF236CBC50BFFECFF5CFE8879DFFD39" blockId="14.[151,1134,322,757]" pageId="14" pageNumber="23">
Cette espèce est confirmée pour 
<collectingRegion id="4989F829C50BFFECFDD9FE887841FEB2" box="[530,620,356,382]" country="Switzerland" name="Geneve" pageId="14" pageNumber="23">Genève</collectingRegion>
, sous ce nom, par 
<bibRefCitation id="EFDC4B3AC50BFFECFC8AFE887ACFFE6D" author="Rezbanyai-Reser L. &amp; Maier E." pageId="14" pageNumber="23" pagination="1 - 118" refId="ref11867" refString="Rezbanyai-Reser L. &amp; Maier E. 2016. Zur Nachtgrossfalterfauna von Sezenove (440 m) bei Bernex, Kanton Genf, Sudwestschweiz, 1979 - 84 (Lepidoptera: &quot; Macroheterocera &quot;). Lepidopterologische Mitteilungen aus Luzern 18: 1 - 118." type="journal article" year="2016">Rezbanyai-Reser &amp; Maier (2016)</bibRefCitation>
, qui l’observent à Sézenove entre fin juillet et fin 
<date id="FFF3100BC50BFFECFCDBFE6A7950FE6C" box="[784,893,390,416]" pageId="14" pageNumber="23" value="1981-08">août 1981</date>
et 1983, mais elle est en réalité connue de toute la 
<collectingCountry id="F35A765BC50BFFECFE30FE44786BFE0E" box="[507,582,424,450]" name="Switzerland" pageId="14" pageNumber="23">Suisse</collectingCountry>
et répertoriée sous le nom de 
<taxonomicName id="4C4D4D48C50BFFECFC76FE457B1CFE28" authority="(Esper, 1790)" baseAuthorityName="Esper" baseAuthorityYear="1790" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Xestia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rhomboidea">
<emphasis id="B939EAD9C50BFFECFC76FE457E40FE0E" box="[957,1133,424,450]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="23">X. rhomboidea</emphasis>
(Esper, 1790)
</taxonomicName>
dans les bases d’info fauna – CSCF (SwissLepTeam 2010, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFDC4B3AC50BFFECFC2DFE277ADBFDCB" author="Wymann H. - P. &amp; Rezbanyai-Reser L. &amp; Hachler M." pageId="14" pageNumber="23" refId="ref12346" refString="Wymann H. - P., Rezbanyai-Reser L. &amp; Hachler M. 2015. Lepidoptera - Noctuidae, Pantheidae, Nolidae: Die Eulenfalter der Schweiz. Fauna Helvetica 28. info fauna - CSCF &amp; SEG, Neuchatel, 959 pp." type="book" year="2015">Wymann et al. 2015</bibRefCitation>
). Bien que cette synonymie ait été utilisée pendant très longtemps, l’examen du matériel 
<typeStatus id="54F68869C50BFFECFED7FDE37B63FDE5" box="[284,334,527,553]" pageId="14" pageNumber="23">type</typeStatus>
d’Esper par 
<bibRefCitation id="EFDC4B3AC50BFFECFE10FDE27854FDE4" author="Hacker" box="[475,633,526,552]" pageId="14" pageNumber="23" pagination="433 - 468" refId="ref10471" refString="Hacker, H. 1998. Die Typen der von E. J. Ch. Esper (1742 - 1810) in seinem &quot; Die Schmetterlinge in Abbildungen nach der Natur &quot; beschriebenen Noctuoidea (Lepidoptera). Esperiana, Buchreihe zur Entomologie 6: 433 - 468." type="journal article" year="1998">Hacker (1998)</bibRefCitation>
a montré qu’elle était fautive: 
<taxonomicName id="4C4D4D48C50BFFECFC0CFDE37E43FDE4" baseAuthorityName="Esper" baseAuthorityYear="1790" box="[967,1134,526,552]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Xestia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rhomboidea">
<emphasis id="B939EAD9C50BFFECFC0CFDE37E43FDE4" box="[967,1134,526,552]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="23">X. rhomboidea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
est en fait un synonyme junior de 
<taxonomicName id="4C4D4D48C50BFFECFDD4FDDD79A6FD87" authority="(Hufnagel, 1766)" baseAuthorityName="Hufnagel" baseAuthorityYear="1766" box="[543,907,560,587]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Xestia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="triangulum">
<emphasis id="B939EAD9C50BFFECFDD4FDDD78ECFD86" box="[543,705,560,586]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="23">X. triangulum</emphasis>
(Hufnagel, 1766)
</taxonomicName>
et 
<taxonomicName id="4C4D4D48C50BFFECFC65FDDD7E6BFD86" baseAuthorityName="Hubner" baseAuthorityYear="1813" box="[942,1094,561,586]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Xestia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="stigmatica">
<emphasis id="B939EAD9C50BFFECFC65FDDD7E6BFD86" box="[942,1094,561,586]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="23">X. stigmatica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
est une espèce valide (
<bibRefCitation id="EFDC4B3AC50BFFECFEA4FDBE7829FDA0" author="Hacker" box="[367,516,594,620]" pageId="14" pageNumber="23" pagination="433 - 468" refId="ref10471" refString="Hacker, H. 1998. Die Typen der von E. J. Ch. Esper (1742 - 1810) in seinem &quot; Die Schmetterlinge in Abbildungen nach der Natur &quot; beschriebenen Noctuoidea (Lepidoptera). Esperiana, Buchreihe zur Entomologie 6: 433 - 468." type="journal article" year="1998">Hacker 1998</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFDC4B3AC50BFFECFDDBFDBE7976FDA0" author="Karsholt O. &amp; Nieukerken E. J. van" box="[528,859,594,620]" pageId="14" pageNumber="23" refId="ref10893" refString="Karsholt O. &amp; Nieukerken E. J. van 2013. Fauna Europaea: Lepidoptera, Moths. Fauna Europaea version 2017.06, https: // fauna-eu. org" type="url" year="2013">Karsholt &amp; Nieukerken 2013</bibRefCitation>
). Pour 
<collectingRegion id="4989F829C50BFFECFC62FDBE7E2EFDA0" box="[937,1027,594,620]" country="Switzerland" name="Geneve" pageId="14" pageNumber="23">Genève</collectingRegion>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFDC4B3AC50BFFECFBC6FDBE7B36FD42" author="Reuteler C. &amp; Rezbanyai-Reser L. &amp; Merz B." pageId="14" pageNumber="23" pagination="326 - 337" refId="ref11713" refString="Reuteler C., Rezbanyai-Reser L. &amp; Merz B. 2012. 8.33. 31. Superfamille Noctuoidea. In: Merz B. (ed.). Liste annotee des insectes (Insecta) du canton de Geneve, pp. 326 - 337. Instrumenta Biodiversitatis 8, Museum d'histoire naturelle, Geneve." type="journal article" year="2012">Reuteler et al. (2012)</bibRefCitation>
mentionnent 
<taxonomicName id="4C4D4D48C50BFFECFE73FD99784FFD42" baseAuthorityName="Esper" baseAuthorityYear="1790" box="[440,610,628,654]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Xestia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rhomboidea">
<emphasis id="B939EAD9C50BFFECFE73FD99784FFD42" box="[440,610,628,654]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="23">X. rhomboidea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
en précisant qu’il s’agit de la même chose que 
<taxonomicName id="4C4D4D48C50BFFECFF5CFD7B7B15FD7C" baseAuthorityName="Hufnagel" baseAuthorityYear="1766" box="[151,312,662,688]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Xestia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="triangulum">
<emphasis id="B939EAD9C50BFFECFF5CFD7B7B15FD7C" box="[151,312,662,688]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="23">X. triangulum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
selon 
<bibRefCitation id="EFDC4B3AC50BFFECFE4BFD7A78A4FD7D" author="Fibiger M. &amp; Skule B." box="[384,649,662,689]" pageId="14" pageNumber="23" refId="ref10169" refString="Fibiger M. &amp; Skule B. 2004. Fauna Europaea: Noctuidae. In: Karsholt O. &amp; Nieukerken E. J. van (eds). Fauna Europaea: Lepidoptera, Moths. Fauna Europaea version 1.5, https: // faunaeur. org" type="url" year="2004">Fibiger &amp; Skule (2004)</bibRefCitation>
. Il s’agit donc de remplacer dans la liste de 
<collectingRegion id="4989F829C50BFFECFF5CFD557AC3FD1F" box="[151,238,697,723]" country="Switzerland" name="Geneve" pageId="14" pageNumber="23">Genève</collectingRegion>
<taxonomicName id="4C4D4D48C50BFFECFF33FD557B88FD1E" baseAuthorityName="Esper" baseAuthorityYear="1790" box="[248,421,696,722]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Xestia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rhomboidea">
<emphasis id="B939EAD9C50BFFECFF33FD557B88FD1E" box="[248,421,696,722]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="23">X. rhomboidea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
par 
<taxonomicName id="4C4D4D48C50BFFECFE15FD5578AFFD1E" baseAuthorityName="Hufnagel" baseAuthorityYear="1766" box="[478,642,696,722]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Xestia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="triangulum">
<emphasis id="B939EAD9C50BFFECFE15FD5578AFFD1E" box="[478,642,696,722]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="23">X. triangulum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(en vertu du principe d’antériorité) et d’y ajouter 
<taxonomicName id="4C4D4D48C50BFFECFF26FD377BABFD38" baseAuthorityName="Hubner" baseAuthorityYear="1813" box="[237,390,731,756]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Xestia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="stigmatica">
<emphasis id="B939EAD9C50BFFECFF26FD377BABFD38" box="[237,390,731,756]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="23">X. stigmatica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(qu’il conviendra de cesser d’appeler 
<taxonomicName id="4C4D4D48C50BFFECFCF3FD3779CFFD38" baseAuthorityName="Esper" baseAuthorityYear="1790" box="[824,994,730,756]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Xestia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="14" pageNumber="23" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rhomboidea">
<emphasis id="B939EAD9C50BFFECFCF3FD3779CFFD38" box="[824,994,730,756]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="23">X. rhomboidea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
).
</paragraph>
